Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.53,0:00:18.72,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,May! Aguente firme!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.73,0:00:21.67,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Muito Obrigado,\N Cecil-Chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.67,0:00:23.80,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Me conceda o poder\N que estou procurando...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.80,0:00:26.13,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hinata! Você tem que acabar\N com isso imediatamente!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.13,0:00:27.71,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Deixe comigo, Bell!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.61,0:00:30.59,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Essa luz...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.59,0:00:31.70,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Rei demônio!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.70,0:00:34.10,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,É nesse local onde você vai morrer!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.43,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Herói!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.05,0:00:45.76,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,O Hinata conseguiu!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.76,0:00:47.23,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Esse é o nosso herói!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.51,0:00:50.21,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Até que enfim a paz voltará à terra...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.76,0:00:51.88,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.88,0:00:53.99,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hinata, o que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.99,0:00:56.18,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Acho que é hora de partir.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.85,0:01:01.77,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Fui convocado do outro mundo para derrotar o Rei Demônio.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.77,0:01:05.00,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Agora que fiz meu trabalho,\N tenho que ir embora.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.00,0:01:06.17,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,O Quê?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.17,0:01:07.42,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.88,0:01:12.48,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mas... Mas então...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.29,0:01:17.80,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,E quanto à nossa promessa de nos casarmos depois de derrotarmos o Rei Demônio?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.80,0:01:19.26,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ahn...?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.75,0:01:20.83,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ah não...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.83,0:01:22.50,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não acho que isso seja...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.50,0:01:24.77,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Só porque você está falando isso desde que nos conhecemos...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.77,0:01:26.97,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Por que não?! Você me odeia\N mesmo ou não?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.97,0:01:28.42,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não, não é isso...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.42,0:01:29.80,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Então, case comigo!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.80,0:01:31.27,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Case comigo! Case comigo! Case comigo!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.01,0:01:37.78,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Uma elfa negra chamada Mariabell. Eu a conheci em outro mundo, e...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.78,0:01:40.59,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,ela está um pouco obcecada por mim... {na verdade ela está muito obcecada e talvez até ser submissa a ele}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.14,0:01:43.09,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu não tenho tempo...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.89,0:01:48.46,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não! Se você desaparecer, Hinata, eu...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.46,0:01:51.10,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não dificulte as coisas para o Hinata.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.10,0:01:52.31,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Cecil...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.31,0:01:55.22,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ela tem razão! Vamos vê-lo\N sair com um sorriso!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.22,0:01:56.79,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mei...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.79,0:01:58.35,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.35,0:02:00.30,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não chore, Bell.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.30,0:02:03.50,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Fico triste por ter\N que deixá-los...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.50,0:02:06.10,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mas um dia nos encontraremos novamente.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.76,0:02:10.29,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.09,0:02:15.61,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Tchau, galera! Até a próxima!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.61,0:02:17.26,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.26,0:02:18.62,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Tome cuidado.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.62,0:02:20.33,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Adeus, Hinata!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.33,0:02:22.49,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Juro que encontrarei um jeito...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.49,0:02:36.90,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Estou saindo.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.29,0:02:44.39,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Já faz um mês que voltei do outro mundo.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.66,0:02:46.75,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Isso estará na prova!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.75,0:02:50.19,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,As coisas voltaram totalmente ao normal.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.67,0:02:54.26,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Uma vida cotidiana segura e tranquila, exatamente como eu queria.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.26,0:02:55.77,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mas..
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.78,0:02:59.77,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,{\fscx84\fscy95}Tchau!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.78,0:02:59.77,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,{\pos(932,95)}Até mais tarde!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.77,0:03:01.97,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,S... Sunohara-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.70,0:03:04.31,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,E.. Eu...
